Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.500 --> 00:00:02.420
Hi guys! Welcome to my kitchen!!!

00:00:02.560 --> 00:00:07.620
Today we prepare three kinds of detox water :)

00:00:07.840 --> 00:00:13.020
Detox waters have a lot of property such us help you to cleanse your body!

00:00:13.340 --> 00:00:18.860
And they are good friends if you are in a diet, during workout or to have something to drink !

00:00:19.180 --> 00:00:23.200
For the first recipe you need 2 oranges  and blueberries.

00:00:23.300 --> 00:00:27.600
For the second one you need 3 rosemary sprigs, a little bit of mint, one cucumber and one lime.

00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:32.220
For the third recipe you need raspberries, strawberries, peaches.

00:00:33.120 --> 00:00:35.760
Now see the first recipe!!

00:00:35.820 --> 00:00:58.660
Slice the oranges and put them into a bottle of water.

00:01:03.480 --> 00:01:09.340
Add blueberries and 1 litre of cold water.

00:01:31.120 --> 00:01:33.240
The first recipe is done!! :)

00:01:39.520 --> 00:01:43.640
For the second recipe prepare 1 cucumber, 1 lime, 3 rosemary sprigs and a little bit of mint.

00:01:43.860 --> 00:01:49.160
Slice the cucumber and put it into the bottle

00:02:12.780 --> 00:02:19.100
Add the rosemary

00:02:39.170 --> 00:02:49.270
Slice the lime and add it to the bottle

00:02:57.280 --> 00:02:59.780
Add the water

00:03:05.000 --> 00:03:13.980
Finally for the last recipe prepare raspberries, strawberries and peaches

00:03:14.820 --> 00:03:16.574
In this case I use two little bottles :)

00:03:19.714 --> 00:03:26.094
Put into the bottles the raspberries

00:03:38.760 --> 00:04:01.600
Slice the strawberries and add to the bottle

00:04:10.520 --> 00:04:22.200
Slice the peaches, put into the bottle and add water

00:05:18.820 --> 00:05:25.340
Put detox waters into the fridge  overnight until drink

